{"tid":669984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳日君為梁寫求情信","createTime":"2018-05-19T03:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T04:45:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1eebc87796f2ded6ad8656d5e7c18ab5e7ff6454","tid":669984,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180519/20395463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180519%2F20395463&d=SNCCr1DqhRAS7ffCpa320AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f83122e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180519%2F20395463&h=099bab7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180519/20395463</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月19日 <br />\n<br />\n陳日君為梁寫求情信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180519/large/19la3p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180519%2Flarge%2F19la3p2.jpg&h=a2f78119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】隨着旺角騷亂案已有裁決，法庭將於稍後宣佈各被定罪被告的判刑，法官須衡量各種求情因素，包括不同人士為被告寫的求情信。天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君（圖）已為梁天琦撰寫求情信，以示對抗爭者的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多次探訪在囚抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n黃傘街頭基督徒基層團體於facebook表示，陳日君一直支持參與抗爭的年輕人，亦曾多次到監獄中探訪梁天琦，以及暴動案、濠涌爆炸品案或其他抗爭案件的在囚抗爭者。現年86歲的陳日君最近曾經病倒，休養期間仍不忘為梁天琦撰寫求情信，再由團體轉交予法院。<br />\n<br />\n求情信對於法官的量刑影響有多大很難評估。在某些案件中，若求情信能說服法官，被告品格良好，所犯罪行完全有別於他平時的表現，或許會成為減刑的理由。所以很多時候，被判罪成的被告都會設法尋求親友以至社會知名人士求情，盡量影響法官。<br />\n<br />\n多年前曾經有一名離婚婦人被控7項騙取綜援罪名成立，被告的5名子女為母親撰寫求情信，結果被告獲輕判240小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n不過也曾經在超市高買被判盜竊罪成的大學生找來女友求情，求情信用了一張印滿公仔的粉藍色信箋，結果反被法官訓斥「求其」。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n騷亂後趨低調　梁天琦藉紀錄片剖白心路歷程　 「無法否定當晚所做一切」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n「黃台仰言論入梁數」不被接納<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【暴動案】拆解梁天琦4項控罪<br />\n<br />\n匿名電郵寄照片至司法機構　揚言「還有很多」　4陪審員庭上遭偷拍　法官報警<br />\n<br />\n由警送返家　可獲貼身保護<br />\n<br />\n意外脫罪　第五被告：無語問蒼天<br />\n<br />\n陪審員一般「免役」兩年<br />\n<br />\n或與「美國隊長」案合併<br />\n<br />\n騷亂後趨低調　梁天琦藉紀錄片剖白心路歷程　「無法否定當晚所做一切」<br />\n<br />\n「黃台仰言論入梁數」不被接納<br />\n<br />\n無悔抗爭　住太空艙免影響家人　第三被告罪成：幫我照顧香港<br />\n<br />\n【動畫●暴動案】「掟磚」示威者自白：唔想似雨傘咁任警察打<br />\n<br />\n棄保潛逃　黃台仰失蹤半年<br />\n<br />\n政府漠視民意　小販難謀生<br />\n<br />\n騷亂後　警購水炮車擴編制<br />\n<br />\n因為時代一點都不溫柔<br />\n<br />\n旺角騷亂案　煽惑暴動罪脫　暴動罪成梁天琦微笑說bye bye"},{"pid":"e41771fdce821b4b75a46c8de21872e28cb36d39","tid":669984,"uid":34410,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"反耶連登仔又要扮睇唔到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e7488ca2074b5931d6e015f5c25eefcd23413f","tid":669984,"uid":135767,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:15:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"549fdbf9f9c1fb3811173796627c82ff5c940e3f","tid":669984,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"696ddccfe0b61cede86fc05190b230ac68de90b5","tid":669984,"uid":35870,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"陳日君令我對宗教重拾信心<br />\n我見到人性光輝嘅一面<br />\n假如耶穌真係存在嘅話<br />\n請憐憫下天琦<br />\nAmen<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a88e405a679cfbcfad06258f2e5cef9fa001d9","tid":669984,"uid":47359,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"696ddccfe0b61cede86fc05190b230ac68de90b5","tid":669984,"uid":35870,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"陳日君令我對宗教重拾信心<br />\n我見到人性光輝嘅一面<br />\n假如耶穌真係存在嘅話<br />\n請憐憫下天琦<br />\nAmen<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"香港係得陳日君似返個神職人員<br />\n其他就舐共潛水尸位素餐"},{"pid":"daad31c42be33b216419be584a7709d2cfed6cd0","tid":669984,"uid":67485,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ab243a836e3618f004f17bd75934d88f9eb75f1","tid":669984,"uid":52701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"陳日君<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a25f99bf601087bbc77359aaa7656b6d7fd41b9","tid":669984,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"陳日君係真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bfc7dbefd0f8ae5e58539d1ccd6156546ca30c","tid":669984,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:38:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38b34ac783641d8843542884ecec77c6b73a1157","tid":669984,"uid":155710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"望下隔黎仆街聖公會Christian, 再望番Catholic"},{"pid":"b9c247e08381a477085c2ca586d96997b1585289","tid":669984,"uid":43119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c9733b4e38f22a2dd72179280f5e411549c6d2","tid":669984,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38b34ac783641d8843542884ecec77c6b73a1157","tid":669984,"uid":155710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"望下隔黎仆街聖公會Christian, 再望番Catholic"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:04:59.000Z","msg":"香港聖公會豬狗不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90abc85c06477880247b9c3522f735f24d5452c4","tid":669984,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}